Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}被捨棄的 面具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像在做噩夢 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了嗎 昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…我說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜…娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥什麼也沒說 什麼也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉所選擇的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在那裡 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉的人身安全有保障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有布里塔尼亞正規軍 還有朱雀在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然作為敵人他們無比棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但棘手也正體現了這保障的可信度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就像我曾經期望過的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使沒有我保護 也已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 聽說這個寺廟是一千年前建的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別提這個了 你看到水槍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明準備了大家的份的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網子 蠟燭 假髮 煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有鈴鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…我們是去修學旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上 我是第二次了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太期待修學旅行 興奮得沒睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…其實就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯真像個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區新總督即將發表就任致辭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請全體同學到禮堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亞第87皇位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替日前殉職的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出任本屆11區總督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雙目失明且腿腳不便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總督？那樣的小女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請各位多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說多多關照…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄得我都亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然匆忙 有一事希望大家能協助於我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算重建日本行政特區
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟說出這種犯忌的話來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本特區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞人和屬區人民將受到平等對待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區人可以重獲日本人之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她剛才說日本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想欺騙我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木朱雀也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也一樣是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是殺戮公主的騎士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出賣ZERO的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然過去在日本特區曾發生過不幸的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我認為其目標並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平等 溫柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請務必加入日本特區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承認彼此的錯誤 一定可以重來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我堅信這點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳 娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會說出重建日本特區…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 尤菲皇姐想做的事是正確的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 錯的不是尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換乘急行列車的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在下車後到站台對面的3號線等待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一站可換乘千京線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,700)}各站停車將在5號站台…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,470)}已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是ZERO 還是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個總督也和殺戮公主尤菲米婭一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 日本人誰也不會參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用甜言蜜語把人引出來 然後趕盡殺絕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少瞧不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 今後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是跟布里塔尼亞決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的Knightmare可只剩下紅蓮一架了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 只要ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城先生說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎麼不見ZERO大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新婚妻子特地趕來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在中華聯邦時他也連封信都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是出軌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 他是騙人的 神樂耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂英雄愛美人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑒於成年男子的生理狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了 你比看起來更成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的時候 感謝你陪伴他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不足掛齒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 卡蓮小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持ZERO大人的三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是三宮女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}註：三宮女是女兒節用來裝飾的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要追尋黑色騎士團 出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精密檢查還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點還是老樣子 他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了完成Conquista…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑麥麵包加黃姜 日本砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混合後再加芥末醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今為止所作所為 都是為了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亞第87皇位繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替日前殉職的卡拉雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉或許已察覺了我的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使如此 她還是說要繼承尤菲的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是為了這 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了先給錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了 窮光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敗家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 你們不也一樣是11區人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要這個 就拿錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本人吃日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是以布里塔尼亞人走狗的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說日本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要布里塔尼亞人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區學生少管人家做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是自願為我所用的 學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我 賤民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我做俯臥撐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科爾恰克先生 您做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下蹲運動 嗥叫 拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回這兒來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 他活著更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…光是不當ZERO那很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也不是多浪漫的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這樣下去 黑色騎士團就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「為娜娜莉而存在的ZERO」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修這麼說呢 瑪莉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道 他到底想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是ZERO…你開始的地方
Comment: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修 我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以靠這個回到懷念的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是失敗了一次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再想作戰計劃挽回不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一樣下命令給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開Knightmare？還是誘餌搜查？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼我都聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安慰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用女人才能做到的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給了我們夢想 就要負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我們騙到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定要把完美的ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任務是監視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是痛苦的重負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是 黑色騎士團是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 娜娜莉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是為了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區就能獲得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也恢復到普通學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福生活就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求幸福 有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會傷害到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還可以將一切歸零
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 只有我不會去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠和哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為何志願提出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出任ZERO復活後的11區總督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前一直受到哥哥的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在雖然他行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他一定還在關注著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要做出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會給哥哥丟臉的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重哦 那面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要肩負整個世界的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是必須有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴艦所屬及航路 與申報有異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請停船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在將進行強行臨檢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將等待十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前所有乘員解除武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到甲板上站好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 大家都去修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要追上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 空無一人的鳥籠正適合現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來了 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修也來放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭用剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？修學旅行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就我們去了 你會哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵不在於去哪裡 而是跟誰一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說能實現願望 就做了試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過怎麼也想不起是跟誰學的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你許了什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經實現了 一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和大家一起放煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有魯路修和羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只折了一隻 所以只實現了魯魯這份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得以前曾跟娜娜莉 朱雀說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若幸福有形態的話 那會是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是了 就像朱雀說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許幸福就像玻璃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為平時從未察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它確實存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證據就是 稍微改變看的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玻璃就會映照出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何東西更雄辯地主張自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說折一千隻這種紙鶴 就能實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉想許什麼願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一個溫柔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的世界就近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使為虛偽的記憶所玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻更顯出透明的琉璃色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我們的友情所感動了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有可愛的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來這裡一起放煙花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定 一定要再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不僅是為了娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 爆破油輪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使敵方聲納失效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下俯配平30度 急速潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的聯絡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依然斷絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該又打算潛入海底逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出動PortmanII
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以被動模式確認
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從動力音判斷應該是水中型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降低深度 被發現就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ASROC（反潛導彈）發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要驚慌 這是無的放矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以θ地點為中心張開包圍網
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能把敵人逼出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦內各部進水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,籐堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一移動會被對方捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Q1 聽到嗎 Q1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下俯配平50度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地點L14急速潛航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 太遲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續投放深水炸彈 保持包圍網
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝向正面 魚雷全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用定時信管設40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了相信他 還有別的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,設定信管後 全彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認魚雷發射音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到敵方位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人在地點L14
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中攻擊 等它浮上我來捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnmingliu\fs16\pos(320,442)\b}火蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnmingliu\fs16\pos(565,442)}藍海豚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Salamander呼叫BlueDolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向定點改變發射角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Portman佈陣區域 傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,網眼不大 別設錯目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是Salamander 已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標設定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈投射管 旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固定錨後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各員 準備承受衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 甲烷水合物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木卿 水泡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 即將翻船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海底湧起巨大的水泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀 這不是叫援軍就能解決的問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合倖存的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將黑色騎士團…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開槍就是違抗君令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定接受娜娜莉總督的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是日本特區的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是投降了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團全員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入日本特區！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許你確實正面帶笑容 正在享受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 那並非真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隱藏在你那笑容背後的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若只有一人知道真相 擁有救贖的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那麼我理當反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.75,0:23:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是名為和平的統治
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蔑視 欺瞞我們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我們視作玩物的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以ZERO的名義…
